DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260525T150000
UID:6973a1a7d2bbe265eb2969b5@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Are you looking to practice your English speaking skills? Come
  out to English Conversation Circle! Meet likeminded peers and practice yo
 ur conversation in a supportive\, casual environment. Please note that thi
 s is not a formal English class.
LOCATION:Lillian H. Smith\, Room B/C
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/6973a1a7d2bbe265eb2969b5
X-SOURCE:Volunteer Toronto
