BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Citizenship Education Circle with CultureLink
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260330T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260330T160000
UID:698de65a7d180d0d48335df2@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:In partnership with CultureLink\, free weekly sessions to help
  you prepare for the Canadian Citizenship Test:\n•	Learn about the test
 ’s content and structure\n•	Get support and tips from CultureLink’s 
 Volunteer Mentors\n•	Practice with sample quizzes\nCutureLink is solely 
 responsible for the protection of personal information collected through t
 he program registration process.\nJan. 12-March 9 Room 1\nMarch 16 eLearni
 ng Lab\nMarch 23 Room 2/3\nMarch 30 Room 2/3
LOCATION:North York Central Library\, Room varies (see program listing)
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/698de65a7d180d0d48335df2
X-SOURCE:Volunteer Toronto
END:VEVENT
