DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260402T150000
UID:69b44c4c8089f23c6761e074@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Practice your English conversation skills in a relaxing enviro
 nment while making new friends and learning what the library has to offer!
 \nBeginner and intermediate learners welcome.  Please note that this is n
 ot a formal English class.\nYou must have a ticket to attend this program.
   Tickets are free and will be available in front of room 101 from 1:30p
 m.  Space is limited.
LOCATION:North York Central Library\, Room 101\, 1st floor
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69b44c4c8089f23c6761e074
X-SOURCE:Volunteer Toronto
